1
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:22,760
Before the elixir's backlash,

2
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:24,690
I should be able to finish them off.

3
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:45,340
Didn't expect it, did you?

4
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:46,760
We still have an ambush.

5
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:47,320
Do it.

6
00:00:49,760 --> 00:00:50,320
Princess,

7
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:52,000
we have no grudges against you.

8
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,360
Why do you want us dead?

9
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:04,599
Yun.

10
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,840
This suicidal move,

11
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,480
as long as I'm here,

12
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,320
I will never let you use it.

13
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:12,520
Yun.

14
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,380
Licheng, are you alright?

15
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,539
Hurry, after them.

16
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,120
You are Su Cheng.

17
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,920
You're awake, miss.

18
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,560
I am Su Cheng.

19
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,280
Earlier,

20
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,480
thank you.

21
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:08,960
My jade pendant...

22
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,000
My jade pendant is gone.

23
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,840
Where are you going?

24
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,880
I'm going to find my jade pendant.

25
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:17,880
Going now is like walking into the tiger's den.

26
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:18,920
Even if I die,

27
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,000
I have to find it.

28
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,240
Miss.

29
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,930
Have a seat first, miss.

30
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,720
Is that jade pendant

31
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,660
really that important to you?

32
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,840
It was left to me by my lover.

33
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,240
One for you, one for me.

34
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,440
We will never be apart.

35
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:53,410
We promised each other a lifetime,

36
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,160
but he died saving me.

37
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:59,079
I couldn't save his life,

38
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,200
nor could I avenge him.

39
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,480
The jade pendant he left behind,

40
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,640
I couldn't protect either.

41
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,120
Your jade pendant.

42
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,360
Why is it with you?

43
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,600
Since it was given by someone you love,

44
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,240
you must keep it safe.

45
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,180
Don't let his true heart down.

46
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,760
Thank you.

47
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,200
But,

48
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,720
they wanted to kill me just now.

49
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,480
You clearly could have escaped.

50
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,410
Why did you come back to save me?

51
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,090
You don't need to ask, miss.

52
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:45,860
It's not the time to tell you the whole truth yet.

53
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,640
The more you know,

54
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,000
the more dangerous it is for you.

55
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,130
You only need to know

56
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,560
that I will do whatever it takes

57
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,920
to help you get revenge.

58
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:01,380
Wait a moment, miss. I'll go start a fire.

59
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:24,840
You have to wait a little longer, miss.

60
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,040
Once the fire is started,

61
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,320
you won't catch a cold.

62
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,240
Miss.

63
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,560
I didn't expect

64
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:52,409
you to look exactly like him when he was young.

65
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:54,720
Who is he?

66
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,930
Let's see where you can run now.

67
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:10,160
How dare you be so insubordinate.

68
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:10,800
At this point,

69
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,260
are you still going to act?

70
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,440
You are not the Beidi Princess at all.

71
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,840
As for Mo Yu,

72
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:18,320
as long as we prove you are an impostor,

73
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:20,320
he won't have any reason to blame us.

74
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,360
Even,

75
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,370
it will be a great achievement.

76
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,930
On what grounds do you say I'm an impostor?

77
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,040
Based on this.

78
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,520
Only one person has the other jade pendant.

79
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:36,360
Could it be that you are Yu?

80
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,800
Stop wasting time with them.

81
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,400
Kill them.

82
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,530
Let's see who dares.

83
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,560
Greetings, God of War.

84
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,280
I told you to save the princess.

85
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:44,610
Is this how you save her?

86
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,820
Since when do you make decisions on your own?

87
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,000
Come back with me.

88
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,680
I...

89
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,360
Are you okay?

90
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:58,900
My Lord.

91
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,800
Whoever takes a step forward

92
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,040
will be killed without mercy.

93
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,000
Yes.

94
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,640
Forgive me, General.

95
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,160
Murdering the princess

96
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,240
is an unforgivable crime.

97
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,970
That woman is not the princess.

98
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,120
Her real name is Mu Jiuyun.

99
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:24,120
This jade pendant is the proof.

100
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:36,320
This jade pendant is Mu Jiuyun's personal belonging.

101
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,440
I am her sister.

102
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,600
I would never be mistaken.

103
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,200
She holds a grudge against my husband and me,

104
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,920
so she pretended to be the princess to seek revenge.

105
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,920
General,

106
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,840
this woman must not be kept.

107
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,600
That's enough.

108
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,600
You may leave.

109
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,480
Yes.

110
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,480
Why is there anyone else

111
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,040
in the study?

112
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:37,840
Don't overthink

113
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:38,970
what you shouldn't.

114
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,680
Have you been the God of War for so long

115
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,120
that you forgot your manners,

116
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,600
Gu Chengyu?

117
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:04,880
Bo, Ying, Rui,

118
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:09,680
Pengyin,

119
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,080
Zijian strengthens its quality.

120
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:11,320
Quan Xuhang

121
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,250
Kun, Quan Xuhang

122
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,300
Quan Yulong

123
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,760
Licheng Lefei

124
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:15,560
Yunlongyinyujiaguangjing

125
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,160
Yunlongyinyujiaguangjing

126
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:19,720
Luoxiaoconglinxunbo

127
